meta-trainerdemo
================

This layer is built up over the four-day Yocto training. It is the single
home for every customization we make in class.

Contents by session
--------------------
  recipes-trainergw/hello/          D1S7  - first custom package
  recipes-trainergw/gw-info/        D1 task - device info script
  recipes-trainergw/packagegroups/  D2S3  - packagegroup bundling
  recipes-kernel/linux/             D2S4, D3S2 - kernel config + hardening

Dependencies
------------
  URI: git://git.yoctoproject.org/poky (meta, meta-poky)
  branch: scarthgap

Adding this layer to a build
----------------------------
  $ bitbake-layers add-layer ../meta-trainerdemo

Maintainer
----------
  Emertxe Information Technologies - training@emertxe.com
